		<item>
			<title>Polling</title>
			<description>&lt;p&gt;I took a political science in college, freshman year at &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lehman.edu/about/&quot;&gt;Lehman College&lt;/a&gt;, in &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/place/Lehman+College,+CUNY/@40.8728933,-73.8966963,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89c2f39b6c3f3913:0xaf1231c8587c56da!8m2!3d40.8728933!4d-73.8945076&quot;&gt;the Bronx&lt;/a&gt;. I was thinking of being a poli sci major. When they got around to polling, it was made clear was you could get people to say whatever you want by how you asked the question.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p&gt;For example if they asked this question.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;ul&gt;&#10;&lt;li&gt;1. Do you think Americans should support the president in times of war, regardless of party? &lt;/li&gt;&#10;&lt;/ul&gt;&#10;&lt;p&gt;And then..&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;ul&gt;&#10;&lt;li&gt;2. Do you approve of how President Biden is handling the war in Ukraine?&lt;/li&gt;&#10;&lt;/ul&gt;&#10;&lt;p&gt;You'd get the patriotic answer inside every American.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;</description>
			<pubDate>Tue, 01 Mar 2022 17:19:35 GMT</pubDate>
			<link>http://scripting.com/2022/03/01/171935.html?title=polling</link>
			<guid>http://scripting.com/2022/03/01/171935.html?title=polling</guid>
			<source:outline text="Polling" created="Tue, 01 Mar 2022 17:19:35 GMT" type="outline" flInCalendar="true" permalink="http://scripting.com/2022/03/01/171935.html?title=polling">
				<source:outline text="I took a political science in college, freshman year at &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lehman.edu/about/&quot;&gt;Lehman College&lt;/a&gt;, in &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.google.com/maps/place/Lehman+College,+CUNY/@40.8728933,-73.8966963,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x89c2f39b6c3f3913:0xaf1231c8587c56da!8m2!3d40.8728933!4d-73.8945076&quot;&gt;the Bronx&lt;/a&gt;. I was thinking of being a poli sci major. When they got around to polling, it was made clear was you could get people to say whatever you want by how you asked the question." created="Tue, 01 Mar 2022 17:19:37 GMT" flInCalendar="true" permalink="http://scripting.com/2022/03/01/171935.html?title=polling#a171937"/>
				<source:outline text="For example if they asked this question." created="Tue, 01 Mar 2022 17:20:21 GMT" flInCalendar="true" permalink="http://scripting.com/2022/03/01/171935.html?title=polling#a172021">
					<source:outline text="1. Do you think Americans should support the president in times of war, regardless of party?" created="Tue, 01 Mar 2022 17:20:26 GMT" flInCalendar="true" permalink="http://scripting.com/2022/03/01/171935.html?title=polling#a172026"/>
					</source:outline>
				<source:outline text="And then.." created="Tue, 01 Mar 2022 17:20:31 GMT" flInCalendar="true" permalink="http://scripting.com/2022/03/01/171935.html?title=polling#a172031">
					<source:outline text="2. Do you approve of how President Biden is handling the war in Ukraine?" created="Tue, 01 Mar 2022 17:20:32 GMT" flInCalendar="true" permalink="http://scripting.com/2022/03/01/171935.html?title=polling#a172032"/>
					</source:outline>
				<source:outline text="You'd get the patriotic answer inside every American." created="Tue, 01 Mar 2022 17:20:42 GMT" flInCalendar="true" permalink="http://scripting.com/2022/03/01/171935.html?title=polling#a172042"/>
				</source:outline>
			</item>
