			<title>The monthly ritual</title>
			<description>&lt;p&gt;The monthly ritual is partially done. I have archived the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/scripting/Scripting-News/blob/master/blog/opml/2022/02.opml&quot;&gt;outline&lt;/a&gt; for February in the GitHub repo.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p&gt;And as a reminder to myself and other Drummer users -- this is what I did for the Daytona part of the rollover.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;ul&gt;&#10;&lt;li&gt;daytona.removeOutlineRefs (&quot;http://drummer.scripting.com/davewiner/blog.opml&quot;)&lt;/li&gt;&#10;&lt;li&gt;daytona.ping (&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/scripting/Scripting-News/master/blog/opml/2022/02.opml&quot;)&lt;/li&gt;&#10;&lt;/ul&gt;&#10;&lt;p&gt;And, amazingly -- it worked. Here's a &lt;a href=&quot;http://daytona.scripting.com/?q=ukraine&amp;collection=scriptingnews&quot;&gt;search&lt;/a&gt; for Ukraine and it finds the refs from February. They moved from the main blog.opml file to the archive file.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;</description>
